Employees stay on the autoCSV import for HRIS/Payroll reasons, but do not have SSO access after their last day. Despite not having SSO access, terminated users can still access Bridge because the Bridge Mobile App doesn't require two-factor authentication after the user's first login. This allows former employees to do the following: 
- view the entire org chart, including their replacement; 
- initiate or continue 1on1s with and assign tasks to any employee, including their replacement;
- send email to any employees via the org chart profile; 
- access proprietary and confidential content as a learner.
